text: Hannes Käsbauer (born 19 October 1986) is a German male badminton player. In 2011, he won bronze medal at the German National Badminton Championships in men's doubles event with Peter Käsbauer. In 2012, he became the runner-up of Slovenia International tournament in mixed doubles event with Kira Kattenbeck. == References == == External links== * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:People from Weiden in der Oberpfalz Category:German male badminton players
